t.  Remio - the best meeting of the week. \n\n\nEngage in Interactive Experiences and Games:\n- Team Puzzle Races\n- Paintball\n- Hide-and-Seek\n- Space-Themed Escape Room\n- Archer Tower Defense\n- Disco Room\n- BarVR\n- Pictionary\n- Red-Light Green-Light\n- Zen Room\n- Basketball\n- and many more arcade-style mini-games\n\n\nCollaborate with Effective VR Tools:\n- Whiteboards\n- Presentation Rooms\n- VR Browser\n- Project Planning Boards\n- Sticky Notes\n- Private Rooms\n- Intimate Boardrooms\n- Gallery Room\n- Aurora Auditorium (large conference venue)\n\n\nSee our website for more details: https://www.remiovr.com/ \nJoin our Discord community: https://discord.gg/8rdzcdmPFZ \n\n\nWe appreciate any feedback or suggestions.\n", "short_description": "Gather. Collaborate. Play.\n\nRemio is the VR app for fun, engaging meetings. Host private sessions from large-scale all-hands events to intimate team-building discussions with your remote team.\n\nMost Popular Games:\n- Team Puzzle Races\n- Paintball\n- Space-Themed Escape Room\n- Archer Tower Defense\n- Basketball\n- Disco Room\n\n\nYou can also use our collaboration tools for whiteboarding, project planning, presentations and brainstorming.\n\nSee our website for more details: https://www.remiovr.com/"}]}, "developer_name": "Remio", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.remiovr.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.remiovr.com/health-disclaimer", "publisher_name": "Remio", "support_website_url": "https://www.remiovr.com/contact-us", "website_url": "https://www.remiovr.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1573854509480616"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED_FOR_SOME_CONTENT", "genres": ["SOCIAL"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommend